column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z, p.petroR5#_r, p.deVRad_r,   p.expRad_r, fsps.logMass, fsps.age, fsps.metallicity,  s.specobjid, s.class, s.z as redshift,  pz.z as photoz,   p.fracDeV_u, p.fracDeV_g, p.fracDeV_r, p.fracDeV_i, p.fracDeV_z FROM fGetNearbyObjEq(#,#,#) n  JOIN PhotoObj AS p on p.objid = n.objid  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = n.objid  JOIN PhotoZ AS pz ON pz.objid = n.objid  JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranWideDust as fsps ON s.specobjid = fsps.specobjid WHERE  s.class = GALAXY
